Subject: Re: [PATCH] Fix memory leak in dlm_add_member() when dlm_node_weight() returns less than zero
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
